      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING SANDCHEZ (1) is in the money every start this course and distance. Is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 2nd over 410m at this track beaten 6 lengths (23.51) behind Pyrenees Ace in a Grade 4/5 on March 3. Can find winning form. WHOPPI DEVERE (6) flew the lids off the inside draw with a fast early split and gave a sight, finishing a 2.75 lengths second (23.44) over 410m at this track. Will give a great sight again. NEEDFUL (5) is a talented dog who is a winner of 12 races but missed the frame last time when fourth at this track (23.56). Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Likely to play a prominent role. LOUIE CABANG (2) won as expected last time – cannot be taken lightly.",
